object.customQuery:
SELECT Policy_Count,Claim_count, MTDWrittenPremiumAmt, MTDEarnedPremiumAmount, LossExpense,LossPaid 
FROM
(select max(Policy_Count) as Policy_Count,max(Claim_count) as Claim_count,
max(MTDWrittenPremiumAmt) as MTDWrittenPremiumAmt,max(MTDEarnedPremiumAmount) as MTDEarnedPremiumAmount,(sum(ULAEExpense)+sum(ALAEExpense)) as LossExpense,sum(LossPaid) as LossPaid from (select coalesce(sum(ULAEExpense),0) as ULAEExpense,coalesce(sum(ALAEExpense),0) as ALAEExpense,coalesce(sum(LossPaid),0) as LossPaid from  (select case when Reservecd in ('Adjustment') then PaidAmt else NULL end as ULAEExpense,
case when ReserveCd='DEFENSE' then PaidAmt else NULL end as ALAEExpense,
case when ReserveCd='Indemnity' then PaidAmt else NULL end as LossPaid
from (SELECT 
  sum(Claimstats_Stg.PaidAmt) as PaidAmt,
Claimstats_Stg.ReserveCd ReserveCd,
Claimstats_Stg.ClaimantTransactionCd ClaimantTransactionCd,
Claimstats_Stg.PolicyNumber PolicyNumber,
case when length(claimstats_stg.policyversion)='1' then concat('00',claimstats_stg.policyversion)
             when length(claimstats_stg.policyversion)='2' then concat('0',claimstats_stg.policyversion)
             else claimstats_stg.policyversion end as policyversion,
Claimstats_Stg.LineCd LineCd,
Claimstats_Stg.RiskCd RiskCd,
Claimstats_Stg.CoverageCd CoverageCd,
Claimstats_Stg.ClaimNumber ClaimNumber,
Claimstats_Stg.LosscauseCd LosscauseCd,
Sum(Claimstats_Stg.PostedRecoveryAmt) as PostedRecoveryAmt,
sum(Claimstats_Stg.ReserveChangeAmt) as ReserveChangeAmt,
Claimstats_Stg.StateCd StateCd, 
 min(Claimstats_Stg.BookDt) as BookDt,
Claimstats_Stg.TransactionNumber TransactionNumber,
min(Claimstats_Stg.AddDt) as AddDt,
min(Claimstats_Stg.EffectiveDt) as EffectiveDt,
Claimstats_Stg.MajorPerilCd MajorPerilCd
from ClaimStats  ClaimStats_stg where adddt>='$$M_StartDt' and adddt<='$$M_EndDt'
group by 
  Claimstats_Stg.PolicyNumber,
claimstats_stg.policyversion,
Claimstats_Stg.LineCd,
Claimstats_Stg.RiskCd,
Claimstats_Stg.CoverageCd,
Claimstats_Stg.ClaimNumber,
Claimstats_Stg.LosscauseCd,
Claimstats_Stg.StateCd,
Claimstats_Stg.ReserveCd,
Claimstats_Stg.TransactionNumber,
Claimstats_Stg.ClaimantTransactionCd,
Claimstats_Stg.MajorPerilCd
)claimstats)T )CS
inner join (select coalesce(sum(MTDWrittenPremiumAmt),0) as MTDWrittenPremiumAmt,
coalesce(sum(MTDEarnedPremiumAmt),0) as MTDEarnedPremiumAmount from policysummarystats where updatedt>='$$M_StartDt' and updatedt<='$$M_EndDt')PSS
on 1=1
inner join (select count(policykey) as Policy_Count from 
(select distinct concat(policynumber,policyversion) as policykey from basicpolicy where cmmcontainer='policy' and systemid in 
(
select SystemId from advrxxchangedbeans where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$M_StartDt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$M_EndDt' and
cmmcontainer='Policy'))x)BP
on 1=1
inner join (select count(claimnumber) as Claim_count from (select distinct claimnumber from claim left join 
              (Select SystemId from claimPolicyInfo where  ClaimPolicyinfo.cmmcontainer='Claim') ClaimPolicyInfo on 
Claim.Systemid=ClaimPolicyinfo.Systemid 
Left join (select systemid,id, riskidref from PolicyRisk) PolicyRisk on claim.riskidref = PolicyRisk.id 
where 
claim.cmmcontainer='Claim' 
and claim.systemid in 
(select SystemId from advrxxchangedbeans where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$M_StartDt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$M_EndDt' and cmmcontainer='Claim' )
)r)C
on 1=1)SRCLoadBalancing
